  "texts": [
    "If the max value of all the softmax probabilities is smaller than the threshold ǫ, the unknown class has been suc- cessfully detected.",
    "Otherwise, the class label is the indices of the maximum softmax probability value.",
    "To demonstrate the efficiency of identifying unknown classes, we conducted experiments on various acoustic datasets.",
    "We trained the network using a self-supervised approach on the DCASE2019 Subtask 1C or MagnT-agATune dataset.",
    "In the supervised approach, each log-mel spectrogram patches produces one class label."
